app.name: Google Cloud Build
app.description:
Google Cloud Build lets you create fast, consistent, reliable builds across all languages. Automatically build containers or non-container artifacts on commits to your GitHub repository. 

Get complete control over defining custom workflows for building, testing, and deploying across multiple environments such as VMs, Serverless, Kubernetes, or Firebase.
